#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc[Quarkus OpenID Connect Authorization code flow mechanism for protecting web applications]"
msgstr "xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc[Quarkus OpenID Connect 授权码流程机制，用于保护 Web 应用程序]"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/security-oidc-auth0-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
